description: This file is a server-side entry point for a Qwik-based web application, responsible for rendering the app outside the browser using server-side rendering (SSR). It imports rendering functions, a manifest, and the main Root component, and exports a default function to generate a render stream with specified options.

methods.name: default
methods.description: Exports a function that takes rendering options and returns a server-side stream rendering the Root component with specified options.
